Package com.xekri.leakvm.sdk.smartlock

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SmartLock.ConnectionCallback
    The ConnectionCallback interface must be implemented by any SmartLock constructor.
    SmartLock.ExtractorDeleteRequest
    The ExtractorDeleteRequest interface is the request for delete an credential.
    SmartLock.ExtractorLoadRequest
    The ExtractorLoadRequest interface is the request for load an credential.
    SmartLock.ExtractorRequest
    The ExtractorRequest interface is the base to make load, delete and save request.
    SmartLock.ExtractorSaveRequest
    The ExtractorSaveRequest interface is the request for save an credential.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SmartLock
    SmartLock class is an useful utility to save, delete and extract a Credential from Google Credentials API
